ould have carried I don't think the Dividians were insane but I don't see a reason for mass suicide if the fire was intentional set by some of the We also don't know that if the fire was intentionally set from inside was it a generally know plan or was this something only an inner circle knew about or was it something two or three felt they had to do with or without Koresch's knowledge blessing I don't know much about Were some people throwing others over Did mothers jump over with their babies in their arms Richard